data.description: Opportunity to own this completely remodeled 4 bdrm 2.5 bath home in the highly sought after International Gardens neighborhood. Sale to consist of 2 parcels thereby creating a lush builders half acre with fruit trees and plenty of space for a pool/patio entertainment and play area. Double door entry from the front terrace patio opens to the foyer, living room & family room with garden views from French doors. Large remodeled open kitchen with breakfast bar plus formal dining area. Bedroom wing on the west side of the house with 3 bdrms/1.5 baths plus master bedroom suite/bath with separate entrance. Storm shutters, inside laundry room plus 2 car garage. Convenient location close to shops, restaurants, excellent schools and nearby expressway.
